$BR
\( \displaystyle \lim_{x\to\infty}\frac{\arctan(x^{$a})}{x^{$b}}\) = \{ ans_rule()\}
$PAR

\( \displaystyle \lim_{x\to 0^+}\sqrt[$b]{x}\ln(x)\) = \{ ans_rule()\}
END_TEXT

